        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Yes, I'd love to participate!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Oh, you're pretty motivated!<CR>Then, let's get you signed up."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "I wasn't sure if we were gonna have enough participants to open the contest, but we do now. Get ready right away!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Wha‐!? Like, right away, right away?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "Of course. Mr. Owner has been way too enthusiastic about it, and has been getting ready for a while now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x1a0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "...So, just go straight to the stage and get ready for your turn, please!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "O-Okay! *sigh* I hope I can do this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x193,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "All right. I'm used to it now,<CR>so I'm always prepared!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x2f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then go straight to the stage, as always, and be ready for your turn, please!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Umm, I think I'll pass this time..."
